 of visitors. It is believed that he is the father of over 30 cubs in the park.   </li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Choti Tara:</strong> Choti Tara is also a famous tigress of Tadoba Andhari Tiger Reserve and she has tried to fight with Maya many times but is still alive. She is Tara’s daughter, so she got the name, Choti Tara. Her mother was killed in a territorial fight. Now Choti Tara is the mother of several cubs and is popular among tourists. She is different from other tigresses because of her flexibility and speed, but now she has been pushed to the park’s fringes, and her two daughters are handling her territory. Those two are now becoming famous among tourists and recently they tried to fight Queen Maya but eventually failed. </li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Conclusion</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We have got information about the most famous tigers of Tadoba, but apart from them, this park is home to many other tigers and animals. If you want to see these tigers in real life from close then you should visit<a href=\"https://tadobapark.com/\"> Tadoba National Park</a>. You can observe them while doing a jeep safari ride inside the park. We hope that you will be able to spot them while doing a Jeep Safari ride.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','The Iconic Tigers of Tadoba: Discover the Most Famous Ones ','','draft','open','open','','','','','2024-04-10 11:54:58','2024-04-10 11:54:58','',0,'https://tadobapark.com/blog/?p=12770',0,'post','',0),(12771,4,'2024-04-10 12:47:39','2024-04-10 12:47:39','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Tadoba National Park is a famous wildlife park located in Maharashtra, India. This park is home to many different species of flora and fauna that are found in huge numbers, which makes it an ideal destination to explore for wildlife and nature lovers. People can explore this place by going on<a href=\"https: