ndia but recently the forest department has allowed night safaris in some national parks. Tadoba is one of the national parks in which people can enjoy a night safari. ','inherit','closed','closed','','12842-revision-v1','','','2024-05-13 12:14:30','2024-05-13 12:14:30','',12842,'https://tadobapark.com/blog/?p=12848',0,'revision','',0),(12850,4,'2024-05-27 10:27:19','2024-05-27 10:27:19','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Tadoba Andhari Tiger Reserve also called<strong> </strong>Tadoba National Park is one of the oldest and largest national parks in the state of Maharashtra, India. This park was established back in 1955 and declared a tiger reserve in 1993. This area has a rich and long history of conservation efforts dating back to the mid-20th century. This park is a famous tourist spot among wildlife lovers because it has a healthy population of Bengal Tigers. This place is one of the best places in India where people can spot some big wild cats in their natural homes.  </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The park has gained popularity and recognition because of its successful tiger conservation programs. Another reason for recognition is that it has made several efforts to protect the habitat and they all were successful attempts. The landscape of Tadoba Andhari Tiger Reserve is best for the wildlife living in it. It has a mix of dense forests, grasslands, and water bodies that are perfect for wild animals.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This famous wild place is located in the Chandrapur district of Maharashtra and encompasses the Tadoba Lake. This lake is one of the major sources of water for the animals living in the park. Along with the big cats, this area is also home to several other species of animals such as leopards, sloth bears, Indian gaur, wild dogs, sambar deer, spotted deer, and many more.&nbsp; This park is home to different types of flora and fauna species with a variety of birds and reptiles. Because of this much wildlife, this is a famous tourist spot for wildlife lovers, photographers, and nature enthusiasts.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This was the information about this fascinating park. Now, let’s know some important tips to enjoy a fabulous trip here</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"23px\"}}} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"font-size:23px\"><strong>Travel To And Fro From Chandrapur To Tadoba: </strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Tadoba is located in Chandrapur district, this is the nearest major town and is relatively straightforward. Traveling to and fro from Tadoba Andhari Tiger Reserve to Chandrapur is very convenient.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>The easiest way of traveling is by hiring a private taxi. The distance from Chandrapur to Tadoba is around 40-45 kilometers. To cover this distance it will take around 1.5 to 2 hours depending on road conditions.&nbsp;</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>If you wish to come by public transport then let me tell you that state-run buses and sharing jeeps are available from Chandrapur to Moharli. Moharli is the main entry gate of this park. Just make sure to check the availability in advance because these buses and jeeps may not be frequent.&nbsp;</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Now, if you want to know how you can reach Chandrapur then you can come here very easily. This place is well connected to major cities like Mumbai, Nagpur, Pune, and Hyderabad. You just have to book your train and after reaching the platform of Chandrapur Railway Station, you can hire a taxi or take a bus to Tadoba.&nbsp;</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>If you’re coming from another country then book your flight for Dr.Babasaheb Ambedkar International Airport. This airport is in Nagpur and after coming here you can take a train towards Chandrapur or you can also come here by taking a taxi or private vehicle.&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"23px\"}}} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"font-size:23px\"><strong>You Need To Choose The Perfect Accommodation </strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Choosing the perfect accommodation totally depends on preferences. Everyone has a different budget and they want different experiences. Some want to stay in luxurious places and enjoy all the modern facilities. Some just need a place that is near to the park, while some want to enjoy the natural surroundings, etc. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>If you’re a nature lover and looking for a natural accommodation where you can spend time in peace with amazing greenery then many tented camps and eco-resorts are available near <strong><a href=\"https://tadobapark.com/\">Tadoba National Park</a></strong>. These options mostly provide comfortable tents that have basic amenities available. By staying in this type of accommodation, you can experience living in the natural surroundings. Just take note of one thing, other amenities like AC, Hot and cold shower, swimming pool, electric kettle, mini fridge, etc will not be given in basic facilities. </li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>If you want a nice comfortable experience then there are many hotels and lodges near Tadoba Andhari Tiger Reserve. They offer a blend of comfort and proximity to the park. By staying near the park you can experience the sound of jungles. While waking up, you can listen to the soothing sounds of birds. These accommodations provide comfy staying options with all the amenities that are needed for a memorable stay.&nbsp;</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>If you want a luxurious experience with all modern stuff, nice infrastructure, and good hospitality then many wildlife resorts and luxurious stays are available near the park. Staying at these places will let you experience world-class facilities. These kinds of resorts have different accommodation options, you can stay in rooms or cottages that are made in themes to provide a nice experience. With important amenities, other facilities like air conditioning, hot water, Wi-Fi, swimming pools, spa services, and recreational activities are offered. You can spend your free time enjoying these activities.&nbsp;</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"23px\"}}} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"font-size:23px\"><strong>Get On The Best Safari Option For A Memorable Trip</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Tadoba National Park is a famous tourist place. Many people come here and the park offers different safari options because of many tourists.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>This park has different tourism zones. People can <a href=\"https://tadobapark.com/tadoba-safari-booking\"><strong>book safaris</strong></a> for core and buffer zones. Core Safaris are conducted in the deeper areas of the forest where the highest number of wildlife is found. Tigers are mostly found in the core areas of this huge park with other animals like leopards, sloth bears, and wild dogs. The jeep safaris will take you to the core zone of the park and you can book your safari for different core gates. Experience guides and drivers will be there on safari with you so that you can get deep knowledge about the park. </li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>People who love to spot wildlife such as deer, monkeys, birds, and smaller carnivores while enjoying the tranquility of the jungle should book a safari for a 